  "instructions": [
    "Pound the garlic and cilantro in a mortar until well combined.",
    "Heat the vegetable oil in a large skillet over medium high heat.",
    "Add the beef to the skillet and cook until browned, about 3 minutes.",
    "Remove the beef from the skillet and set aside.",
    "Add the sliced red onion to the skillet and cook until softened, about 3 minutes.",
    "Add the diced tomatoes to the skillet and cook for an additional 2 minutes.",
    "Return the beef to the skillet and stir in the soy sauce, vinegar, salt, and black pepper.",
    "Cook for an additional 2 minutes, until the beef is cooked through.",
    "Serve the lomo saltado on a wooden board, garnished with chopped cilantro."
